&quot; You have called my child, and I have answered. What can I help you with my dear?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamznrobin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AmznRobin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#993300>(8/19/02 7:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A calling</span><hr size=1> She blinked, looking over at the goddess, surprized that it had actually worked. Gotta remember that for the next time, she thought. She bowed slightly to the goddess.<br>
  &quot;I want to become pregnant my goddess, I want a baby girl to help further and strengthen the Nation,&quot; she looked up at her. &quot;Tell me what I can do to please you, so that you might help me...please,&quot; she added quickly, just incase. <p>Robin ~Credendo Vides~
